#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid "The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n\n"
"#### Build your own app\n\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr "Har bir Twenty ish maydoni ishlaydigan asosiy ma’lumotlar modeli.\n\n"
"#### \"Poydevor\" nimani anglatadi\n\n"
"Har bir Twenty ish maydoni obyektlarning ushbu to‘plami bilan boshlanadi. Ular sizning CRM tuzilishingizni, shu jumladan munosabatlar, faollik va hisobotlarni belgilaydi. Qolgan hamma narsa, jumladan bozor ilovalari, AI agentlari va maxsus obyektlar ularga ulanadi.\n\n"
"#### Kiritilgan obyektlar\n"
"- **People & Companies**: kontakt va hisob yozuvlari\n"
"- **Opportunities**: savdo voronkangiz\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: faollik va kuzatuv vazifalari\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: avtomatlashtirish va hisobotlar\n\n"
"Ushbu ilovani olib tashlasangiz, Twenty ning qolgan qismi tayanadigan asosdan mahrum bo‘ladi.\n\n"
"#### O‘zingizning ilovangizni yarating\n\n"
"Twenty’ni o‘z obyektlaringiz, maydonlaringiz, mantiq funksiyalaringiz yoki AI ko‘nikmalaringiz bilan kengaytiring. Yangi ilovani bitta buyruq bilan shablon asosida yarating:\n\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n\n"
"So‘ng papka ichida:\n\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n\n"
"To‘liq yo‘lko‘rsatma uchun [Boshlash bo‘yicha qo‘llanma](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) bilan tanishing va `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIlariga oid ma’lumot uchun [Ilovalar yaratish](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) bo‘limiga qarang."

